trans-unit.source: Defines a method for adding the <see langword="DocumentStructure" /> part of XML Paper Specification (XPS) to an XPS package.
trans-unit.target: Definiert eine Methode zum Hinzufügen des <see langword="DocumentStructure" />-Teils der XML Paper Specification (XPS) in ein XPS-Paket.

trans-unit.source: For more information about the `DocumentStructure` element of an [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xps](~/includes/tla2sharptla-xps-md.md)] package, see chapter 9 in the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_xps](~/includes/tlasharptla-xps-md.md)] specification, which you can obtain at [XPS: Specification and License Downloads](http://www.microsoft.com/whdc/xps/downloads.mspx).
trans-unit.target: Weitere Informationen zu der `DocumentStructure` Element des ein [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xps](~/includes/tla2sharptla-xps-md.md)] Verpacken, finden Sie in Kapitel 9 der [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_xps](~/includes/tlasharptla-xps-md.md)] -Spezifikation, die Sie, am erhalten können [XPS: Spezifikation und License Downloads](http://www.microsoft.com/whdc/xps/downloads.mspx).

trans-unit.source: Adds the <see langword="DocumentStructure" /> part of [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_xps](~/includes/tlasharptla-xps-md.md)] to an [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xps](~/includes/tla2sharptla-xps-md.md)] package.
trans-unit.target: Fügt den <see langword="DocumentStructure" />-Teil von [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_xps](~/includes/tlasharptla-xps-md.md)] zu einem [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xps](~/includes/tla2sharptla-xps-md.md)]-Paket hinzu.

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.XpsStructure" /> that represents the <see langword="DocumentStructure" /> part of an [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xps](~/includes/tla2sharptla-xps-md.md)] package.
trans-unit.target: Eine <see cref="T:System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.XpsStructure" />, die das <see langword="DocumentStructure" />-Part eines [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xps](~/includes/tla2sharptla-xps-md.md)]-Pakets darstellt.

trans-unit.source: For more information about the `DocumentStructure` element of an [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xps](~/includes/tla2sharptla-xps-md.md)] package, see chapter 9 of the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_xps](~/includes/tlasharptla-xps-md.md)] specification, which you can obtain at [XPS: Specification and License Downloads](http://www.microsoft.com/whdc/xps/downloads.mspx).
